About

MacThrottle (http://github.com/dkong/MacThrottle) is a simple GUI for ipfw to limit internet download bandwidth.

Components

Uses the BDAuthorize sample code (http://www.bdunagan.com/2008/11/23/sudo-nstasks-with-mac-os-xs-security-framework/) with modifications for root access.

